From cou.: 5 The paper is organized as follows: in chapter II the simulation method is briefly described. Results for the sedimentation problem are presented in chapter III and compared to real-space confocal microscopy data. The instability and the concomitant solvent flow fields and colloidal velocity correlations are discussed. Finally, we present our conclusions in chapter IV.
From Soup: 5 The paper is organized as follows: in chapter II the simulation method is briefly described. Results for the sedimentation problem are presented in chapter III and compared to real-space confocal microscopy data. The instability and the concomitant solvent flow fields and colloidal velocity correlations are discussed. Finally, we present our conclusions in chapter IV.
